```
class Person {
    int id;
    public Person(int id) {
        this.id = id;
    }
}

class Employee extends Person {
    String name;
    public Employee(int id) {
        super(id);
    }
    public Employee(int id, String name) {
        super(id);
        this.name = name;
    }
}
```

